'''Senior Dark Side Adept''' was a title given to the highest-ranking of [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine's]] [[Dark side adept/Legends|Dark Side Adepts]]. It was they who were charged in training the several of [[Imperial Sovereign Protector]]s into the ways of the [[Dark side of the Force/Legends|dark side of the Force]].

